## Ignore Visual Studio Temporary Files, Builds, and Metadata
.vs/
[Dd]ebug/
[Dd]ebugPublic/
[Rr]elease/
[Re]leasePublic/
x64/
x86/
build/
bld/
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Ll]og/
[Ll]ogs/

## Ignore NuGet Packages
*.nupkg
## The packages folder can be ignored because of Package Restore
**/packages/*
## except build/, which is used as an MSBuild target.
!**/packages/build/
## Uncomment if using NuGet Signatures
#*pubgrub

## Ignore User-Specific settings
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## Ignore OS-generated files
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

## Ignore local config / secrets
appsettings.Development.json
secrets.json

